description: Quality furniture that you don't find in just any old furniture store. A bit pricey, but you get what you pay for. The store is easy to navigate and the sales people are friendly without being pushy. They have so many pieces I like, I think I need a bigger apartment!
This paint is excellent. pricey but well worth it. excellent gloss and colour retention
Incredible and beautiful home decor. Great staff and great selection in product Great place to pick up cute gifts. A little more on the expensive side, but well worth it
